                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainties are estimates of author's",
                "lack of knowledge of the beam energy at the center of",
                "the scattering chamber due to the uniformity of nylon",
                "windows, lack of information on the exact amount of",
                "carbon deposited on these windows at the time of",
                "observation, and fluctuations in the accelerating",
                "potential."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
